#. <section class="sutta" id="sn40.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn40.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 40"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 40"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Moggallānavagga"
msgstr "1. By Moggallāna"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Ākāsānañcāyatanapañhāsutta → ākāsaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn40.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Ākāsānañcāyatanapañhāsutta"
msgstr "5. A Question About the Dimension of Infinite Space"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn40.5:1.1"
msgid "“‘Ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ, ākāsānañcāyatanan’ti vuccati."
msgstr "“They speak of this thing called the ‘dimension of infinite space’."

msgctxt "sn40.5:1.2"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho ākāsānañcāyatananti?"
msgstr "What is the dimension of infinite space?"

msgctxt "sn40.5:1.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi:"
msgstr "It occurred to me:"

msgctxt "sn40.5:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘idha bhikkhu sabbaso rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā paṭighasaññānaṃ atthaṅgamā "
"nānattasaññānaṃ amanasikārā ananto ākāsoti ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ upasampajja "
"viharati."
msgstr ""
"‘It’s when a mendicant—going totally beyond perceptions of form, with the "
"ending of perceptions of impingement, not focusing on perceptions of "
"diversity—aware that “space is infinite”, enters and remains in the "
"dimension of infinite space."

msgctxt "sn40.5:1.5"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati ākāsānañcāyatanan’ti."
msgstr "This is called the dimension of infinite space.’"

msgctxt "sn40.5:1.6"
msgid ""
"So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, sabbaso rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā paṭighasaññānaṃ "
"atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṃ amanasikārā ananto ākāsoti ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ "
"upasampajja viharāmi."
msgstr ""
"And so … I was entering and remaining in the dimension of infinite space."

msgctxt "sn40.5:1.7"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, iminā vihārena viharato rūpasahagatā saññāmanasikārā "
"samudācaranti."
msgstr ""
"While I was in that meditation, perceptions and attentions accompanied by "
"forms beset me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn40.5:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho maṃ, āvuso, bhagavā iddhiyā upasaṅkamitvā etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha came up to me with his psychic power and said:"

msgctxt "sn40.5:2.2"
msgid "‘moggallāna, moggallāna."
msgstr "‘Moggallāna, Moggallāna!"

msgctxt "sn40.5:2.3"
msgid ""
"Mā, brāhmaṇa, ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ pamādo, ākāsānañcāyatane cittaṃ saṇṭhapehi, "
"ākāsānañcāyatane cittaṃ ekodiṃ karohi, ākāsānañcāyatane cittaṃ samādahā’ti."
msgstr ""
"Don’t neglect the dimension of infinite space, brahmin! Settle your mind in "
"the dimension of infinite space; unify your mind and immerse it in the "
"dimension of infinite space.’"

msgctxt "sn40.5:2.4"
msgid ""
"So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, aparena samayena sabbaso rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā "
"paṭighasaññānaṃ atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṃ amanasikārā ananto ākāsoti "
"ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"And so, after some time … I entered and remained in the dimension of "
"infinite space."

msgctxt "sn40.5:2.5"
msgid "Yañhi taṃ, āvuso, sammā vadamāno vadeyya … pe … mahābhiññataṃ patto”ti."
msgstr ""
"So if anyone should be rightly called a disciple who attained to great "
"direct knowledge with help from the Teacher, it’s me.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn40.5:2.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
